invalid type: string "- Penalty for violation: Imprisonment up to 5 years and/or fine up to ₹1 lakh.\n- Citizens can approach the National Green Tribunal (NGT) directly.(no lawyer needed).\n- Application fee: ₹1,000 (individuals).\n- NGT has power to award compensation, impose penalties, issue injunctions.\n- File at: ngt.gov.in or approach NGT benches in New Delhi, Bhopal, Pune, Kolkata, Chen